    <h1>Kevin Heuzey</h1>
    <h2>Blockchain Infrastructure Architect & Tech Entrepreneur</h2>

    <p>Kevin Heuzey is an Israeli tech entrepreneur, crypto infrastructure architect, and the founder of <a href="https://www.integrity.farm">Integrity.farm</a> — a blockchain protocol that redefines Bitcoin mining through on-chain emulation. By eliminating the need for physical hardware while leveraging real-time Bitcoin network data, Integrity.farm enables programmable, Bitcoin-backed incentives for Web3 platforms, gaming ecosystems, and decentralized economies.</p>

    <p>In 2015, he launched Ethereum Garden, one of the first decentralized Ethereum mining clusters in Eastern Europe. The project, fully bootstrapped in Odessa, Ukraine, scaled to over 2,500 GPUs and was profiled by <a href="https://telegraf.com.ua/ukr/statti/2018-05-30/5911124-ethereum-garden-naysmilivishiy-mayning-proekt-skhidnoi-evropi">Telegraf</a><sup>[1]</sup>.</p>

    <p>In 2016, he joined the <a href="https://www.timesofisrael.com/situation-gets-hackathoner-to-make-riot-warning-app/">Israel Tech Challenge</a><sup>[2]</sup>, where he trained with Unit 8200 alumni<sup>[3]</sup> in AI, cybersecurity, and decentralized systems.</p>

    <p>In 2017, he joined <a href="https://hacken.io">Hacken</a><sup>[4]</sup> as a strategic advisor and served as a jury member at the <a href="https://ctftime.org/event/672/">HackIT Cup</a><sup>[5]</sup>, an event sponsored by <a href="https://fenbushi.vc">Fenbushi Capital</a><sup>[6]</sup> and attended by Vitalik Buterin.</p>

    <p>In 2018, he contributed to Web3 cybersecurity discussions alongside <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phil_Zimmermann">Phil Zimmermann</a><sup>[7]</sup> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Wozniak">Steve Wozniak</a>.</p>

    <p>In December 2017, he launched a 2.5 MW Tier 4 Bitcoin mining facility at the <a href="https://www.bell-labs.com/">Nokia Paris-Saclay campus</a><sup>[8]</sup> and co-founded the Blockchain Research Institute, which he directed until 2024.</p>

    <p>In 2024, French deep-tech firm <a href="https://www.vistory.com">Vistory</a> joined as seed investor for Integrity.farm and integrated it with industrial blockchain infrastructure like <a href="https://www.eurosatory.com/en/innovations/mainchain/">MainChain</a><sup>[9]</sup>.</p>

    <p>Today, Kevin builds verifiable, trustless infrastructure for decentralized finance, and advises a European aerospace firm on blockchain-secured autonomy and defense systems.</p>

    <p><a href="https://kevinheuzey.com">kevinheuzey.com</a> | <a href="https://www.integrity.farm">integrity.farm</a></p>
